Symbol.Script_3D:
! Rack-Mounted Water Filter
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, dTHeight, unID: unID=unID+1

ROTx 90 ADDz -dTDepth/2 PRISM_ 16, dTDepth, -dTWidth/2, 0, 15, -dTWidth/2, frameThick, 15, -dTWidth/2+frameThick, frameThick, 15, -dTWidth/2+frameThick, dTHeight, 15, dTWidth/2-frameThick, dTHeight, 15, dTWidth/2-frameThick, frameThick, 15, dTWidth/2, frameThick, 15, dTWidth/2, 0, 15, dTWidth/2-legThick, 0, 15, dTWidth/2-legThick, frameThick, 15, dTWidth/2-frameThick*2, frameThick, 15, dTWidth/2-frameThick*2, dTHeight-frameThick, 15, -dTWidth/2+frameThick*2, dTHeight-frameThick, 15, -dTWidth/2+frameThick*2, frameThick, 15, -dTWidth/2+legThick, frameThick, 15, -dTWidth/2+legThick, 0, 15 PRISM_ 4, 0.35*DRate, -dTWidth/2+frameThick*2, frameThick+0.305*HRate, 15, -dTWidth/2+frameThick*2, frameThick*2+0.305*HRate, 15, dTWidth/2-frameThick*2, frameThick*2+0.305*HRate, 15, dTWidth/2-frameThick*2, frameThick+0.305*HRate, 15 DEL 2
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN FOR i=1 TO 4 ADD -dTWidth/2+frameThick*2+cRad+0.055*WRate+(cRad*2+0.01*WRate)*(i-1), -0.35*DRate+dTDepth/2+cRad+0.025, frameThick*2+0.305*HRate CYLIND dTHeight-frameThick*3-0.385*HRate, cRad DEL 1 NEXT i
ADD 0, -0.35*DRate+dTDepth/2+cRad+0.025, dTHeight-frameThick-0.08*HRate PRISM_ 4, 0.08*HRate, -dTWidth/2+frameThick*2, -cRad-0.01*DRate, 15, -dTWidth/2+frameThick*2, cRad+0.01*DRate, 15, dTWidth/2-frameThick*2, cRad+0.01*DRate, 15, dTWidth/2-frameThick*2, -cRad-0.01*DRate, 15 DEL 1 ELSE ADD 0, -0.35*DRate+dTDepth/2+cRad+0.025, frameThick*2+0.305*HRate PRISM_ 4, dTHeight-frameThick*3-0.305*HRate, -dTWidth/2+frameThick*2, -cRad-0.01*DRate, 15, -dTWidth/2+frameThick*2, cRad+0.01*DRate, 15, dTWidth/2-frameThick*2, cRad+0.01*DRate, 15, dTWidth/2-frameThick*2, -cRad-0.01*DRate, 15 DEL 1 ENDIF
ADD -dTWidth/2+0.12+frameThick, -dTDepth/2+0.02, dTHeight BLOCK 0.15, 0.30, 0.065 ADDx 0.20 BLOCK 0.15, 0.30, 0.065 DEL 2
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 1, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConPosZ_3=ConPosZ_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConEdit_3 = 1, ConPosX_4=ConPosX_4, ConPosY_4=ConPosY_4, ConPosZ_4=ConPosZ_4, ConLength_4=ConLength_4, ConEdit_4 = 1, ConPosX_5=ConPosX_5, ConPosY_5=ConPosY_5, ConPosZ_5=ConPosZ_5, ConLength_5=ConLength_5, ConEdit_5 = 1 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Rack-Mounted Water Filter
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2, -dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 dTWidth/2, dTDepth/2, unID: unID=unID+1
SET FILL gs_fill_type
PEN gs_cont_pen IF gs_fill_pen THEN PEN gs_fill_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 3+32, 4, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PEN gs_cont_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 2, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConShow_1 = 0, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConShow_2 = 0, ConEdit_2 = 1, ConPosX_3=ConPosX_3, ConPosY_3=ConPosY_3, ConLength_3=ConLength_3, ConShow_3 = 0, ConEdit_3 = 1, ConPosX_4=ConPosX_4, ConPosY_4=ConPosY_4, ConLength_4=ConLength_4, ConShow_4 = 0, ConEdit_4 = 1, ConPosX_5=ConPosX_5, ConPosY_5=ConPosY_5, ConLength_5=ConLength_5, ConShow_5 = 0, ConEdit_5 = 1 DEL 1
END
